description:
Daysky D Book Air Notebook
Daysky D Book Air is equipped with a 14.0 inch FHD LED display, brings your photos and videos to life. Designed with HDMI output, allows you to connect it to monitors, TV or projectors, perfect for creating your personal home theater. 

Main Features:
Intel Celeron 3855U Dual Core 1.6GHz
Ultra-low-voltage platform and dual-core processing provide maximum high-efficiency power to go. Intel Turbo Boost Technology delivers dynamic extra power when you need it
14.0 inch FHD LED Screen with 1920 x 1080 Resolution
Offering good experience for watching videos and browsing the Web. The 1920 x 1080 resolution screen boasts impressive high-quality images
4GB DDR4 RAM for Advanced Multitasking, up to 8GB
Substantial high-bandwidth RAM to smoothly run your games, photos and video-editing applications, as well as multiple programs and browser tabs all at once
128GB SSD ROM Storage Capacity
Provides room to store pictures, videos, music and more
Camera for Photos and Face-to-face Chat
0.3MP front camera let you capture memorable moments or chat with friends
HDMI Output Expands Your Viewing Options
Connect the tablet to an HDTV or high-definition monitor to set up two screens side by side or just enlarge pictures
